title: Coach Conversations, Injury Update & Problems in Texas
description:
Wendi Nix, Joey Galloway and Greg McElroy discuss problems at Texas A&M after the Aggies lost to Mississippi State on Saturday. Plus, who is Jalen Milroe and should he be the starting quarterback for Alabama? Also, Adam Rittenberg joins to show to take a deep dive into Wisconsin's and Colorado's head coaches being fired over the weekend and the candidates who could be next for the job. And, who's the front-runner of the Big 12 now that Oklahoma is no longer ranked?
